com.percussion.services.contentmgr
Interface IPSContentPropertyConstants

public interface IPSContentPropertyConstants

Common node property names defined here. Inclusion here is because it is either a special property for which there is no corresponding field in the system definition, or because it requires special handling due to the mapping from PSComponentSummary.

Author:
dougrand
